    "description": "<p>   <strong> Mediatech Marketing Pte Ltd </strong>offers a comprehensive range of Auto Identification Data Capture products, Point-of-Sales solutions, technology and support necessary to provide integrated industry-specific data management systems for mission critical business applications.  Embarking on full range of innovative and high-performance products such as bar code scanners, label printers, hand-held mobile computers, RFID readers, point-of-sales and wireless communications networks for voice and data; Mediatech bridges the connection for data and decision makers for greater productivity, competitiveness and profitability.   Please visit us at www.mediatec.com.sg </p>  ",
